au.com.cybersearch2.classyjpa.entity

Class PersistenceDao<T,ID>

  • java.lang.Object
    • au.com.cybersearch2.classyjpa.entity.PersistenceDao<T,ID>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.j256.ormlite.dao.CloseableIterable<T>, Iterable<T>

    public class PersistenceDao<T,ID>
extends Object
implements com.j256.ormlite.dao.CloseableIterable<T>
    Adapted com.j256.ormlite.dao.RuntimeExceptionDao to throw javax.persistence.PersistenceException instead. Proxy to a Dao that wraps each Exception and rethrows it as PersistenceException. 

     PersistenceDao<Account, String> accountDao = PersistenceDao.createDao(connectionSource, Account.class);

    Author:
    graywatson
